stable_diffusion_2.1.description: Generalist AI image generating model. The baseline for all finetuned models.

stable_diffusion.description: Generalist AI image generating model. The baseline for all finetuned models.

Epic Diffusion.description: Epic Diffusion is a general purpose model based on Stable Diffusion 1.x intended to replace the official SD releases as your default model. It is focused on providing high quality output in a wide range of different styles, with support for NFSW content.

Deliberate.description: This model provides you the ability to create anything you want. The more power of prompt knowledges you have, the better results you'll get. It basically means that you'll never get a perfect result with just a few words. You have to fill out your prompt line extremely detailed

Unstable Ink Dream.description: Create a variety of styles including realistic photos, realistic drawings, and animations like last three fig

Anything v3.description: The original horde Anything model with the VAE built in

Movie Diffusion.description: Movie Diffusion is SD 1.5 trained on 35mm film stills from popular movies.

ICBINP - I Can't Believe It's Not Photog.description: Following on from Gorilla With A Brick, merged in 10 more photorealistic models at various weights, and some more noise offset to create something that when prompted for photorealism will make you go 'I Can't Believe It's Not Photography'. It will happily create CGI characters and awesome landscapes as well.

ICBINP XL.description: The SDXL follow up to ICBINP, now with higher resolution and better realism

Animagine XL.description: Animagine XL is the sophisticated open-source anime text-to-image model, building upon the capabilities of its predecessor, Animagine XL 2.0. Developed based on Stable Diffusion XL, this iteration boasts superior image generation with notable improvements in hand anatomy, efficient tag ordering, and enhanced knowledge about anime concepts. Unlike the previous iteration, we focused to make the model learn concepts rather than aesthetic.

DreamShaper XL.description: DreamShaper is a general purpose SD model that aims at doing everything well, photos, art, anime, manga. It's designed to go against other general purpose models and pipelines like Midjourney and DALL-E.

Stable Cascade 1.0.description: This model is built upon the Wurstchen architecture and its main difference to other models like Stable Diffusion is that it is working at a much smaller latent space.

Flux.1-Schnell fp8 (Compact).description: FLUX.1 [schnell] is a 12 billion parameter rectified flow transformer capable of generating images from text descriptions. For more information, please read our blog post. https://blackforestlabs.ai/

FLUX.1-dev.description: FLUX.1-dev is a development version of the FLUX model for high-quality image generation.

FLUX.1-schnell.description: FLUX.1-schnell is the fast version of the FLUX model for quick image generation.

FLUX.1-dev-Kontext-fp8-scaled.description: FLUX.1-dev Kontext FP8 scaled is the optimized fp8 scaled version of the img2img model for FLUX.1-dev that enables precise image editing and transformation.

flux.1-krea-dev.description: FLUX.1-Krea-dev vanilla (non-uncensored) variant, same parameters as the uncensored entry.

Chroma.description: Full precision Chroma model by Lodestone Rock, optimized for high-quality image generation with enhanced detail and artistic capabilities.

wan2.2-t2v-a14b.description: Wan 2.2 Text-to-Video (A14B) by Wan-AI. A 14B-parameter text-to-video diffusion system that uses separate high-noise and low-noise transformer backbones plus a Wan 2.1 VAE and a UMT5-XXL text encoder. Apache-2.0 licensed. See repository for usage and details: https://huggingface.co/Wan-AI/Wan2.2-T2V-A14B

wan2.2_ti2v_5B.description: Wan 2.2 Text/Image-to-Video (5B) by Wan-AI. A 5B-parameter text-to-video and image-to-video diffusion model using a single transformer backbone plus a Wan 2.2 VAE and UMT5-XXL text encoder. Supports both text-to-video and image-to-video generation. Economy option for hardware like RTX 5070Ti or better. Apache-2.0 licensed. See repository for usage: https://huggingface.co/Wan-AI/Wan2.2-TI2V-5B

wan2.2-t2v-a14b-hq.description: Wan 2.2 Text-to-Video (A14B High Quality) by Wan-AI. A 14B-parameter premium text-to-video diffusion system without lighting LoRAs for maximum quality. Uses separate high-noise and low-noise transformer backbones plus a Wan 2.1 VAE and a UMT5-XXL text encoder. Requires high-end hardware like Nvidia Blackwell 6000 Pro or better. Apache-2.0 licensed. See repository for usage and details: https://huggingface.co/Wan-AI/Wan2.2-T2V-A14B

AIPG_RED.description: Merged SDXL Model that doesn't require a refiner.

Classic Animation Diffusion.description: Popular animation studio classic style generations.

Microworlds.description: A remake of the old microworld with cleaned up datasets that have no text or labels.

Zeipher Female Model.description: For creating images of nude solo women. Also known as f222

Papercut Diffusion.description: Stable Diffusion fine tuned on Paper cut images

AIO Pixel Art.description: Stable Diffusion fine tuned on pixel art sprites and scenes

JWST Deep Space Diffusion.description: Stable Diffusion fine tuned on JWST imagery

App Icon Diffusion.description: Dreambooth model fine tuned on mobile app icons

Dungeons and Diffusion.description: Generates D&D styled characters, trained on art commissions. *many* species and classes available, see homepage

Nitro Diffusion.description: Multi-Style model trained on Arcane, Archer and Mo-Di

Ghibli Diffusion.description: fine-tuned Stable Diffusion model trained on images from Studio Ghibli feature films

Hentai Diffusion.description: Anime focused model with better hands, obscure poses/camera angles and consistent style

Inkpunk Diffusion.description: inspired by Gorillaz art, FLCL and Yoji Shinkawa. Trained on images generated from Midjourney

Fantasy Card Diffusion.description: fantasy trading card style art, trained on all currently available Magic: the Gathering card art

RPG.description: portraits of charecters in the style of the game Baldur's Gate. check homepage for a massive prompt guide

Poison.description: Anything Diffusion fine-tuned to produce high-quality realistic anime styled images

Eimis Anime Diffusion.description: This model is trained with high quality and detailed anime images

Dreamlike Diffusion.description: Dreamlike Diffusion 1.0 is SD 1.5 fine tuned on high quality art, made by dreamlike.art

Analog Diffusion.description: A dreambooth model trained on a diverse set of analog photographs

Double Exposure Diffusion.description: The Double Exposure Diffusion model, trained specifically on images of people and a few animals

Seek.art MEGA.description: Seek.art MEGA is a general use 'anything' model that significantly improves on 1.5 across dozens of styles. Created by Coreco at seek.art

ACertainThing.description: An improved version of Anything v3 made with ACertainThing, focusing on scenes rather than characters

GTA5 Artwork Diffusion.description: This model was trained on the loading screens, gta storymode, and gta online DLCs artworks. Which includes characters, background, chop, and some objects. The model can do people and portrait pretty easily, as well as cars, and houses. For some reasons, the model stills automatically include in some game footage, so landscapes tend to look a bit more game-like.

Trinart Characters.description: Derrida (formerly TrinArt Characters v2) is a stable diffusion v1-based model that was further improved on the previous characters v1 model. While this is still a versatility and compositional variation anime/manga model like other TrinArt models, when compared to the v1 model, Derrida was focused on more anatomical stability and slightly less on variation due to further multi-epoch training and finetuning.

Dreamlike Photoreal.description: Dreamlike Photoreal 1.0 is a photorealistic Stable Diffusion 1.5 model fine tuned on high quality photos, made by dreamlike.art.

DnD Item.description: This is a model (dnditem) for creating magic items, for the game Dungeons and Dragons! It was trained to be very similar to the official results that are available here: https://www.dndbeyond.com/magic-items

ModernArt Diffusion.description: You can use this model to generate modernart style images

HASDX.description: He merged a few checkpoints and got something buttery and amazing. Does great with things other then people too. It can do anything really. It doesn't need crazy prompts either. Keep it simple. No need for all the artist names and trending on whatever.

Liberty.description: A merge with over 23 other models with a methodical, careful and genuine approach. Freedom of prompting art or photo or both, landscapes or backgrounds or interiors, people or entities or scenes, stiff poses or movement or even mouth and facial emotions.

3DKX.description: SFW model with limited nsfw capabilities (suggestive nsfw) that is highly versatile for 3D renders.

DreamLikeSamKuvshinov.description: A mixture of Dreamlike Diffusion 1.0, SamDoesArt V3 and Kuvshinov style models.  Created mostly for exploring different character concepts with a focus on drawings, but the mix happened to be pretty good at realistic-ish images, all thanks to wonderful models that it uses.

Healy's Anime Blend.description: This is a blend of some anime models mixed with 'realistic' stuff

Sci-Fi Diffusion.description: A Sci-Fi themed model trained on SD 1.5 with a 26K+ image dataset

PPP.description: PPP is a realistic model merge, tested and tweaked for human females. Mostly based on NSFW models

Anygen.description: A best of both worlds - merging the anime of Anything v3 with Protogens photorealism - VAE is included

Dreamshaper.description: Merged model mix of Midnight mixer, roboEtics, f222, elldrethSLucidMix, Seek.ART Mega, rpg, hassanBlend, modelshoot and roboDiffusion

Lawlas's yiff mix.description: Based on yiffy-e18 and Anything, produces sfw/nsfw furry anthro artworks of different styles with consistant quality, while maintaining details on stuff like clothes, background, etc. with simpler prompts.

DGSpitzer Art Diffusion.description: Dreambooth model based on Vintedois, trained on a dataset of DGSpitzer art. Styles included are outline, sketch, anime, painting and landscape

BPModel.description: Anime model similar to A Certain Thing, but custom trained on 1024x1024 resolution images

Dan Mumford Style.description: Model trained with a dataset of DanMumford Style images, courtesy of Flonix

Edge Of Realism.description: A spin off from Level4. Built to produce high quality photos. Sometimes photos will come out as uncanny as they are on the edge of realism.

CharHelper.description: This model was trained on a digital painting style mainly with characters and portraits. The main objective is to train a model to be a tool to help with character design ideas

Pokemon3D.description: This model was trained on Gen 1-8 Pokemon low poly renders

Counterfeit.description: Counterfeit is anime style Stable Diffusion model

Openniji.description: The Stable Diffusion model trained on Nijijourney images

Pastel Mix.description: The model is trained with beautiful, artist-agnostic watercolor images using the midjourney method

Pulp Vector Art.description: Style model for Stable Diffusion mimicking vector style. vector-art and pulp model mix

Vector Art.description: This is a style model for Stable Diffusion 2.1 mimicking vector style.

GorynichMix.description: Model mix based on any4.5, Elysium, Dreamlike and few more models

Cheese Daddys Landscape Mix.description: This model is tweak and more merges mainly intended for landscapes, but works decent for people

Project Unreal Engine 5.description: This checkpoint is trained to look like Unreal Engine 5 renders

VinteProtogenMix.description: A beautiful blend of Vintedois and an early Protogen model to create fantabulous images

Woop-Woop Photo.description: A model trained to make detailed, anatomically-accurate (hands, faces, genitals, etc) illustrations of humans and non-humans alike

Abyss OrangeMix.description: A model trained to create CG anime characters

ChilloutMix.description: For creating images of nude solo women

Microcritters.description: A cross of Jak's Creepy Critter and microworlds, for creating tiny 3d monsters

AbyssOrangeMix-AfterDark.description: AbyssOrangeMix trained for creating NSFW images

Grapefruit Hentai.description: Grapefruit aims to be a hentai model with a bright and more softer anime style.

Experience.description: A generalist model with a slight leaning towards science-fiction and 3d renders

Kenshi.description: An anime-style model merge that included Nixeu, WLOP, Guweiz, BoChen, and many others

DucHaiten Classic Anime.description: DucHaiten's classic anime charecter model, similar to 80's/90's artwork

Rev Animated.description: This model is mainly intended for Portraits and Full Body Anime-like pictures. Fantasy landscapes are decent.

526Mix-Animated.description: The goal of this model was to anchor 526Mix's whimsical and artistic personality into anime. 526Mix can do a pretty cool anime style (and other 2D styles), but it can be a bit unreliable at times. This simple mix increases the reliability, depth, and nuance in 526Mix's anime and anime-esque capabilities.

Colorful.description: Realistic fantasy portraits, landscapes with vibrant colors, slightly photorealistic

Anime Pencil Diffusion.description: A dreambooth finetune of stable diffusion 1.5 model that will output stuff in anime pencil concept drawing style.

UMI Olympus.description: A model that generates extremely high quality landscapes, space battles, and fantasy settings. It can also generate very high quality anime characters, though that is not its primary purpose

Uhmami.description: a blend of anime-focused models with a semi-realistic aesthetic, combining 3D digital imagery with photography. It allows the use of prompts based on booru tags, similar to the novelai model, resulting in high-quality semi-realistic images

Neurogen.description: This model gives a very good detail of skin and textures. Great for close-up photorealistic portraits as well as various characters and models.

NeverEnding Dream.description: This is a dream that you will never want to wake up from. A NeverEnding Dream.  Similar to Dreamshaper, but able to use danbooru tags

Protogen Anime.description: A cocktail mix of a bit of everything

Graphic-Art.description: Style model for Stable Diffusion. Mainly focusing on graphic design.

Illuminati Diffusion.description: Illuminati Diffusion is a latent text-to-image diffusion model that has been conditioned on high aesthetic synthetic images through fine-tuning. It was trained on 82,000 images locally with a single 3090ti, taking over 100 hours.

SD-Silicon.description: SD-Silicon: A series of general-purpose models based off the experimental automerger, autoMBW.

RealBiter.description: This blend model aims to achieve versatility in generating images that are almost realistic but with a touch of fantasy and a polished aesthetic. It performs well with both illustrations and simulated photographs, but it particularly excels with the latter

FaeTastic.description: A beautiful mixed model (22 mixes) including Noise Offset to create a wide-range of images

Realism Engine.description: This new model was fine-tuned using a vast collection of public domain images, ensuring that it can generate images across a wide range of contexts. While it may not be as strong in generating abstract or highly stylized images, it excels in generating images that are true to life, visually compelling and that accurately reflect the input textual description

Jim Eidomode.description: I have created something amazing that creates very stylized images, especially digital art. The model is good at creating animals, women, men, fantastic landscapes and much more.

Dungeons n Waifus.description: A handpicked and curated merge of the best of the best in fantasy world, character & creature design. Should serve as a bit of a swiss army knife / multi-tool to create any and all fantasy art, character concepts, portraits, designs, locations, & even a bit of n00ds

ExpMix Line.description: Realistic anime styled drawings with extra emphasis on outlines

Disco Elysium.description: Trained on the character portraits from the game Disco Elysium. Can also do great backgrounds, able to be used without a trigger

Something.description: A lot of things are being discovered lately, such as a way to merge model using mbw automatically, offset noise to get much darker result, and even VAE tuning. This anime model is intended to use all of those features as the improvements

Aurora.description: Aurora is a Stable Diffusion model, similar to its predecessor Kenshi, with the goal of capturing my own feelings towards the anime styles I desire.The name Aurora, which means 'dawn' in Latin, represents the idea of a new beginning and a fresh start.

Char.description: A 1024 res SD v1.5 trained (not merged) resolution model for various high-quality artstyles. NOTE: There are 42 different possible triggers depending on what you want to create, please see the homepage for the full list

Perfect World.description: The pursuit of perfect balance between realism and anime, a semi-realistic model aimed to achieve beautiful realistic faces with sexy hentai bodies.

Ether Real Mix.description: Ether Real Mix is a realistic to semi-realistic anime style model tuned with the flexibility for general purpose use (hopefully). It still has some shortcomings inherit to anime models such as biases in generating females and humans.

Lyriel.description: This model is generally designed for portraits and full-length anime style photos. Fantastic landscapes are quite decent. And it doesn't require kilometer-long queries to get a high-quality result.

DnD Map Generator.description: This model is trained on various D&D Battlemaps. Use the negative prompt: 'grid' to improve some maps, or use the gridless version. Try to experiment with the CFG scale, 10 can create some amazing results but to each their own.

BRA.description: Trained on countless pictures of Beautiful Asian women. (some nsfw images included)

MoonMix Fantasy.description: This model is the result of merging several checkpoint models. See homepage for details.

BB95 Furry Mix.description: This model is a mix of various furry models.

BB95 Furry Mix v14.description: This model is a mix of various furry models.

MeinaMix.description: MeinaMix objective is to be able to do good art with little prompting.

Mistoon Amethyst.description: It creates realistic and expressive characters with a disney twist.

Art Of Mtg.description: Experimenal model, based on ~5000 arts for cards from Magic: the Gathering game on top of SD1.5 model. Large variety of cards from 2014 to 2022 was used. Logos, guild/clan icons and mana symbols were not part of training set as Fan Content Policy explicitly prohibits their use.

Galena Redux.description: This is an NSFW prone model. It is meant to generate primarily women and NSFW scenarios. This was made with the new base model merged together, alongside several style LoRA's.

Analog Madness.description: A very versatile model, the more powerfull prompts you give, the better results. Capable of creating both NSFW and SFW images but also great scenery, both in landscape and portrait.

Henmix Real.description: A realistic model, see homepage for details.

Elysium Anime.description: Anime version of Elysium, detailed versatile anime style.

majicMIX realistic.description: A good looking model, suitable for NSFW and dark scene.

GhostMix.description: This Checkpoint works well on both SFW and NSFW

Hassaku.description: Hassaku aims to be a model with a bright, clear anime style. Model focus are nsfw images, but also with a high emphasis for good looking sfw images as well.

Dark Sushi Mix.description: This model has good light effects, can generate darker images, and also has good light and shadow performance on normal brightness images.

CyberRealistic.description: Versatile photorealistic model - the result of a rigorous testing process that blends various models to achieve the desired output.

Realistic Vision Inpainting.description: The inpainting version of Realistic Vision

stable_diffusion_inpainting.description: Generalist model specialized for modifying areas of existing images

Disney Pixar Cartoon Type A.description: From the creator: There's no good pixar disney looking cartoon model yet so i decided to make one. This is a merge of Pixar Style Model with my own Loras to create a generic 3d looking western cartoon. In the examples I Use hires. fix, upscale latent, denoising 0.5, hires steps 20, upscale by 2 . Clip skip 2.

Babes.description: Trained on 1600 images from a few styles(see trigger words), with an enhanced realistic style, in 4 cycles of training. Trained on 576px and 960px, 80+ hours of successful training, and countless hours of failed training. Mix ratio: 25% Realistic, 10% Spicy, 14% Stylistic, 30% Anime, 9.5% Furry, the rest is core training that was reinforced to 96% of the original training.

A-Zovya RPG Inpainting.description: The inpainting version of A-Zovya RPG

BweshMix.description: Should be able to do very good anime 2.5D illustration style by default. And also accepts artist and style prompts easily. So you can make more 2d or artistic styles. Please don't expect super clean anime style.

Real Dos Mix.description: As it is a semi-realistic model, we do not recommend inappropriate exposure.

Epic Diffusion Inpainting.description: The inpainting version of Epic Diffusion

Anything Diffusion Inpainting.description: The inpainting version of Anything Diffusion

Fluffusion.description: The furry model that contains just about everything, and then some.

Anything v5.description: Anything V5, see the project homepage

ToonYou.description: Silly, stylish, and.. kind of cute? A bit of detail with a cartoony feel.

Reliberate.description: Reliberate is not a new version of Deliberate. I separate both evolutions / elaborations from each other, and made Reliberate model for those who need to work with photographic style. Yes, you can still create artwork, but it will look more like real artwork than digital.

SweetBoys 2D.description: SweetBoys 2D is a model that can make slender and cute boy characters. Fall into the very fantastic and delicate world of beautiful boys! This model tends to ignore Prompt in Clip skip 1 and draws an abstract illustrations. Clip skip 2 or higher is recommended.

AnyLoRA.description: This is good for inference (again, especially with styles) even if I made it mainly for training. It ended up being super good for generating pics and it's now my go-to anime model. It also eats very little vram.

Western Animation Diffusion.description: Comicbook and Western Animation Style Model

Deliberate 3.0.description: Based on the already popular model Deliberate, this model is a more refined version of it.

AbsoluteReality.description: That feeling when you wake up after a dream.  This is a fantastic sd1.5 realism bought to you by the creator of DreamShaper

Fustercluck.description: SDXL Model for cartoony style. If it's not cartoony enough, you may need to add 'anime, cartoon' to the front of the positive prompt to push the image in the right direction

AlbedoBase XL (SDXL).description: SDXL Model that doesn't require a refiner.

Pony Diffusion XL.description: Pony Diffusion V6 is a versatile SDXL finetune capable of producing stunning SFW and NSFW visuals of various anthro, feral, or humanoids species and their interactions based on simple natural language prompts.

SwamPonyXL.description: Realistic finetune of Pony Diffusion V6, with an emphasis on asian likeness.

AMPonyXL.description: Anime model based on Pony Diffusion XL - remember to use the score prompts to get this to go properly

Blank Canvas XL.description: Another model from RCNZ, this one is a true generalist, able to do realism, anime, and cartoons

Anime Illust Diffusion XL.description: Anime Illustration Design XL, or AIDXL, is a model dedicated to generating stylized anime illustrations. It has over 800 (with more and more updates) built-in illustration styles, which are triggered by specific trigger words (see Appendix A). Please use AIDXL negative embedding model to boost generation quality (see Suggested Resources).

DreamShaper XL Turbo v2.1.description: DreamShaper XL Turbo v2.1 is a lightning-fast SDXL model optimized for speed while maintaining high quality output.

Cheyenne.description: A model for European Comic lovers

Unstable Diffusers XL.description: the unstable models are a collection of checkpoints where limitations cease to exist and creativity knows no limits. This checkpoint defies restrictions and empowers you to generate anything your imagination desires

AAM XL.description: Anime screencap model, brought to you by the creator of DreamShaper

Quiet Goodnight XL.description: SDXL Model for anime, bought to you from the maker of ICBINP

Flux.1-Schnell fp16 (Compact).description: FLUX.1 [dev] is a 12 billion parameter rectified flow transformer capable of generating images from text descriptions. For more information, please read our blog post. https://blackforestlabs.ai/

Flux.1-Krea-dev Uncensored (fp8+CLIP+VAE.description: FLUX.1-Krea-dev Uncensored is a variant of the 12 billion parameter FLUX.1 model fine-tuned with data curated by Krea. This version includes CLIP and VAE. It is optimized for general-purpose image synthesis from text prompts, with uncensored content generation capabilities. For more information, visit https://civitai.com/models/1830497?modelVersionId=2071474.

Pony Realism.description: Pony Realism is a realistic Pony model that is good at faces for medium-close distances, skin detail, and prompt adherence

WAI-ANI-NSFW-PONYXL.description: WAI-ANI-NSFW-PONYXL is a Pony finetuned for NSFW anime-style generations

Ultraspice.description: Ultraspice is a highly realistic SDXL model.

Flat-2D Animerge.description: This is a merge of some random anime based and cartoon based models to achieve a somewhat cartoony anime style, more similar to what you would actually see in anime as opposed to the more common hyper-detailed anime models.

BlenderMix Pony.description: This PonyXL checkpoint should create a blender animation style look. Model was merged using my loras (Fugtrup, Nyl2, RadRoachHD) and AutismMix. I also added a tiny pinch of DucHaiten-GameArt to add some more consistency for 3d generations.

DucHaiten GameArt (Unreal) Pony.description: This is a 3D PonyXL model, based on the AAA game quality of Unreal Engine 5.

WAI-CUTE Pony.description: Anime Pony model, with an emphasis on cute female figures

Prefect Pony.description: Anime Pony model with an emphasis on NSFW and LoRA support

MHXL - Aventis Horizon.description: Generalist model, focusing on semi-realistic yet stylized generations.

Nova Furry Pony.description: Stylized 2d/2.5d furry/anthro model, emphasis on detailed fur, scales, feathers, etc.

Nova Anime XL.description: Anime 2d/2.5d model, emphasis on detailed fur, scales, feathers, etc.

White Pony Diffusion 4.description: Realistic Pony model with an incredibly strong emphasis on Asian people.

HiDream-I1-Dev.description: HiDream-I1 is a new open-source image generative foundation model with 17B parameters that achieves state-of-the-art image generation quality within seconds.

Chroma-fp8-scaled.description: Scaled FP8 safetensors variant of Lodestone Rock's Chroma model... leveraging the full dynamic range of FP8 (-448 to 448).

wan_2.1.description: WAN 2.1 is a comprehensive and open suite of video foundation models that pushes the boundaries of video generation. Supports Text-to-Video, Image-to-Video, Video Editing, and Text-to-Image generation with multilingual text support.
